               tools to generate OTU count data from a set of diverse
               underlying network topologies. SPIEC-EASI outperforms
               state-of-the-art methods to recover edges and network properties
               on synthetic data under a variety of scenarios. SPIEC-EASI also
               reproducibly predicts previously unknown microbial associations
               using data from the American Gut project.",
